    * Automating compilation with Makefile
        * Makefile structure 
            - Define Variables
            - Create source/objects files and run object separatly 
            - `make` to compile
            - `make start` to execute the program
            - Compilation of src files
            - Compilation of run.cpp file
            - `make clean` to clean obj and bin files
            
        

